00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:31.680
less than half of that of the average New Zealander

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.160
and that goes to the core of what

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:34.840
you're always talking about

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:37.560
which is that those who are at the top

00:07:37.560 --> 00:07:39.840
