and they're gonna buy anything that has a return of

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:46.640
you know

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:47.840
just over 5% you know

00:11:47.840 --> 00:11:49.680
unless the house price is above here

00:11:49.680 --> 00:11:50.400
they're gonna buy it

00:11:50.400 --> 00:11:52.360
so you have to pay this enormous amount

00:11:52.560 --> 00:11:53.600
but then what you

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:55.840
what you get is this kind of perverse reaction

00:11:55.840 --> 00:11:56.720
which is

00:11:57.920 --> 00:12:01.280
because people know then that unless you own wealth

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:02.880
