00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:56.160
Americans who are watching

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:59.280
this is not a problem that you can run away from

00:12:59.280 --> 00:13:00.600
because it is a global problem

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:01.960
it's a worldwide phenomenon

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:03.280
Yeah and again

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:05.520
it's gonna require probably

00:13:05.520 --> 00:13:08.080
if we're going to do wealth taxation properly

00:13:08.200 --> 00:13:10.280
global coordination. Yeah.

00:13:10.280 --> 00:13:11.360
But again you know

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:13.960
as I think you frequently point to

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.600
it might be really hard to do

